body:
### Hi.
I'm a Peruvian developer interested in programming, Linux, Hacking and AI. I tackle on challenging problems and try to solve them with code. If you want to know more about me [here](http://jnreynoso.github.io/CV.pdf) is my cv. Also you can stop and say hello at jeanalessi.reynoso@yahoo.com.

### About
My name is Jean Reynoso, I have 20 years and live in Lima, I'm a programmer who has over 3 years of experience in software development. I started when I was very young to develop apps in Visual FoxPro, expanding my knowledge to all the other web system and achieving eventually more elaborated structures. I am currently working at [Wunderman Phantasia](http://www.wundermanphantasia.pe/) as a Full stack developer.

### Skills
* Javascript
* Python
* CSharp
* Visual Basic
* Java
* C/C++
* HTML-CSS
* SQL
* PHP
